headline: Walmart Stock, Not Target, Could Drive Consumer Staples’ Momentum
summary: Consumer staples like Walmart could be poised to benefit.  This sector has a number of things going for it beyond diversification: Concerns about a possible economic slowdown should benefit retailers known for value and bargains, and technical signals suggest future gains.  The weekly chart of the Consumer Staples Select Sector SPDR exchange-traded over the past year reveals a bullish ascending triangle forming.
